DGAPI Course Finder - License Terms

This repository contains the Course Finder tool powered by DiscGolfAPI.

TERMS OF USE

You can use this tool and code freely in:
- Websites
- Apps
- Maps and directories
- Tools and dashboards

ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT

If you use DiscGolfAPI data via this tool, you must include visible attribution:

"Course data supplied by DiscGolfAPI"

Where possible, include a link to https://discgolfapi.com

Attribution must be:
- Visible to users
- Placed near the data
- Not hidden in metadata only

RESTRICTIONS

You may not:
- Republish the full DiscGolfAPI dataset as a competing service
- Misrepresent the data as your own
- Remove or obscure attribution
- Use the data in a misleading way

WARRANTY DISCLAIMER

Data is provided as-is. No warranty is given for:
- Accuracy
- Completeness
- Availability

You should verify course details independently before relying on them.

CHANGES

DiscGolfAPI reserves the right to:
- Update the data structure
- Change available fields
- Limit or remove access

COMMERCIAL USE

For commercial use or questions, contact DiscGolfAPI.

